title: [Pawn and Thrift, Backroom]
description: Haphazardly organized to provide a modicum of maneuverability, the rear of the tiny cottage contains even more pawned goods.  Sunlight filters through an oval window set high on the east wall, highlighting the slightly used wares for sale.
